---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Music | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Music studies, atmospheres, and selected pieces from Kreativ Sound."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/music/"
  activeNav="music"
>
  <section class="card page-main music-page-modern">
    <div class="music-hero">
      <div class="music-hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Music</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Artist pages tied to the wider sound world.</h1>
        <p class="page-lead">Olaru and Rethyn are both personal music projects by Andrei Olaru, built with heavy use of Kreativ Sound samples, sounds, and presets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="music-hero-panel">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Listening paths</p>
        <h2>Two artist directions</h2>
        <p><strong>Olaru</strong> carries the ambient and melodic side. <strong>Rethyn</strong> carries the darker, signal-shaped electronic direction. Both pull directly from the same Kreativ Sound palette used across the catalog.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="music-artist-stack">
      <section class="music-artist-shell" aria-labelledby="olaru-heading">
        <div class="music-artist-head">
          <div>
            <p class="learn-card-kicker">Artist</p>
            <h2 id="olaru-heading">Olaru</h2>
            <p class="music-artist-intro">Ambient pieces, studies, and melodic sketches published on Bandcamp, shaped heavily with Kreativ Sound textures, samples, and presets.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Visit Bandcamp
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="music-grid">
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/memories" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1549831212_2.jpg" alt="Memories album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Memories</h3>
            <p>Sketchbook ambience and melodic memory fragments.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/trees" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a0092871322_2.jpg" alt="Trees album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Trees</h3>
            <p>Organic studies with texture, distance, and color.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/vision-no-return" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1511504117_2.jpg" alt="Vision No Return album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Vision No Return</h3>
            <p>Melancholic motion and hazier cinematic drift.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/nightfall" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1183385430_2.jpg" alt="Nightfall album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Nightfall</h3>
            <p>Low-light ambience and restrained melodic cues.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/selected-ghosts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1961746094_2.jpg" alt="Selected Ghosts album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Selected Ghosts</h3>
            <p>Atmospheric fragments and shadowed piano distance.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
          <a class="music-card" href="https://olaru.bandcamp.com/album/ambitones" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2196578473_2.jpg" alt="Ambitones album cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Album</span>
            <h3>Ambitones</h3>
            <p>Minimal tonal studies with spatial restraint.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open on Bandcamp <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="music-artist-shell music-artist-shell-alt" aria-labelledby="rethyn-heading">
        <div class="music-artist-head">
          <div>
            <p class="learn-card-kicker">Artist</p>
            <h2 id="rethyn-heading">Rethyn</h2>
            <p class="music-artist-intro">Electronic sketches and signal-driven pieces under the Rethyn moniker, also built with strong use of Kreativ Sound sounds and presets.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="button secondary" href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/7iwBaUeCQYimysZAoKh42X" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Open Spotify
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="music-grid music-grid-single">
          <a class="music-card music-card-featured" href="https://music.amazon.com/artists/B0GV4RM888/rethyn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="music-card-image" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31zy-G17D-L._SX354_SY354_BL0_QL100__UXNaN_FMjpg_QL85_.jpg" alt="Holo Signal cover" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="learn-card-kicker">Single</span>
            <h3>Holo Signal</h3>
            <p>Released March 27, 2026. Includes <strong>Holo Signal</strong> and <strong>Holo Drift</strong> as the first public Rethyn release.</p>
            <span class="music-card-link">Open artist page <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
